# 🤖 AI Chat & Age Prediction Agent

An AI Agent built with **n8n** and **Google Gemini** that can chat with users and predict a person's age using the **Agify API**.

---

## 📌 Project Overview

This project demonstrates how an AI Agent can use an external API through the **HTTP Request Tool** in n8n.

Instead of relying only on the LLM's knowledge, the agent intelligently decides when to call an API, extracts the required information from the user's prompt, and returns a natural language response.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 💬 AI Chat using Google Gemini
- 🌐 HTTP Request Tool integration
- 🧠 Automatic tool calling
- 🔍 Name extraction from user prompts
- 📊 Live age prediction using Agify API
- 🤖 Natural language responses

---

## 🏗️ Workflow Architecture

```text
When Chat Message Received
        │
        ▼
    AI Agent
    ├── Google Gemini Chat Model
    └── HTTP Request Tool
            │
            ▼
        Agify API
```

